###############################################
# 9. Multi-Organization Support
###############################################

### List my organizations (just this one so far)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/my-organizations

### Switching to an org I'm not a member of should 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/switch-organization
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Switching to my own org should succeed (no-op but exercises the endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/switch-organization
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}"
}

### Setting my own org as primary (already is) should succeed
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/primary-organization
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}"
}

